[Amit Varma]: and Shobhana Rai kind of columnist, I would just tell my readers that please don't be

00:53:09.480 --> 00:53:13.140
[Amit Varma]: an Amit Verma kind of columnist because people who write about politics and economics do

00:53:13.140 --> 00:53:14.880
[Amit Varma]: nothing to change the world.

